TestNG annotation hierarchy:

@BeforeSuite
@BeforeTest
@BeforeClass
@BeforeMethod

@Test(Attributes(enable, alwaysRun, groups))

@AfterMethod
@AfterClass
@AfterTest
@AfterSuite

Cross Browser Testing from local: Running multiple tests with different parameter for browser name and using @Parameters
 annotation, where our driver will initiate based on the browser value.

